#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.26:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga "
msgstr "3. Persons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Sevitabbasutta "
msgstr "26. Associates "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.125, sc1
msgctxt "an3.26:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“These three people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.3"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "There is a person you shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend. "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.4"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "There is a person you should associate with, accompany, and attend. "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.5"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "There is a person you should associate with, accompany, and attend with honor and respect. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.26:1.6"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo? "
msgstr "Who is the person you shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend? "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo hīno hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya. "
msgstr "It’s someone who is inferior in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.26:1.8"
msgid "Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na payirupāsitabbo aññatra anuddayā aññatra anukampā. "
msgstr "You shouldn’t associate with, accompany, or attend such a person, except out of kindness and compassion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.26:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo? "
msgstr "Who is the person you should associate with, accompany, and attend? "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sadiso hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya. "
msgstr "It’s someone who is similar in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.3"
msgid "Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "You should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person. "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

#. VAR: pavattinī → pavattanī (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.26:2.5"
msgid "Sīlasāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ sīlakathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no pavattinī bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissati. "
msgstr "Thinking, ‘Since our ethical conduct is similar, we can discuss ethics, the conversation will flow, and we’ll both be at ease. "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.6"
msgid "Samādhisāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ samādhikathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no pavattinī bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since our immersion is similar, we can discuss immersion, the conversation will flow, and we’ll both be at ease. "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.7"
msgid "Paññāsāmaññagatānaṃ sataṃ paññākathā ca no bhavissati, sā ca no pavattinī bhavissati, sā ca no phāsu bhavissatīti. "
msgstr "Since our wisdom is similar, we can discuss wisdom, the conversation will flow, and we’ll both be at ease.’ "

msgctxt "an3.26:2.8"
msgid "Tasmā evarūpo puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "That’s why you should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.26:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo? "
msgstr "Who is the person you should associate with, accompany, and attend with honor and respect? "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo adhiko hoti sīlena samādhinā paññāya. "
msgstr "It’s someone who is superior in terms of ethics, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.3"
msgid "Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "You should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person with honor and respect. "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

# NOTE: BB has “in various respects” for tattha tattha, but this is too weak. It is an emphatic universal, as seen in https://suttacentral.net/pi/sn1.26 unlike the sun an moon, fire shines both day and night; https://suttacentral.net/pi/sn17.8 the mangu jackal is afflicted everywhere he goes; https://suttacentral.net/pi/thag2.32 dwellings are always impermanent; or https://suttacentral.net/pi/thag1.1, not having insight in various respects, but everywhere.
msgctxt "an3.26:3.5"
msgid "Iti aparipūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmi; "
msgstr "Thinking, ‘I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of ethical conduct I haven’t yet fulfilled, or support with wisdom in every situation the ethical conduct I’ve already fulfilled. "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.6"
msgid "aparipūraṃ vā samādhikkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā samādhikkhandhaṃ tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmi; "
msgstr "I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of immersion I haven’t yet fulfilled, or support with wisdom in every situation the immersion I’ve already fulfilled. "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.7"
msgid "aparipūraṃ vā paññākkhandhaṃ paripūressāmi, paripūraṃ vā paññākkhandhaṃ tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmīti. "
msgstr "I’ll fulfill the entire spectrum of wisdom I haven’t yet fulfilled, or support with wisdom in every situation the wisdom I’ve already fulfilled.’ "

msgctxt "an3.26:3.8"
msgid "Tasmā evarūpo puggalo sakkatvā garuṃ katvā sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo. "
msgstr "That’s why you should associate with, accompany, and attend this person with honor and respect. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.26:3.9"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasminti. "
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.126, sc4
msgctxt "an3.26:4.1"
msgid "Nihīyati puriso nihīnasevī, "
msgstr "A man who associates with an inferior goes downhill, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.2"
msgid "Na ca hāyetha kadāci tulyasevī; "
msgstr "but associating with an equal, you’ll never decline; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.3"
msgid "Seṭṭhamupanamaṃ udeti khippaṃ, "
msgstr "following the best, you’ll quickly rise up, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.26:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā attano uttariṃ bhajethā”ti. "
msgstr "so you should keep company with people better than you.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.26:4.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
